transcript.sentence: A pair of hands, palms up,
is shown in front of a blue sky with clouds.
The hands have a colorful map of the world painted on them.
Many different hands are placed on Top of one another, representing teamwork, support or friendship.
A beautiful brick paved pathway slopes up,
then into a hairpin turn,
and back up and away from the camera,
it disappears behind an old fancy building.
The sky is dark with clouds, and there are potted plants, ivy and a few trees. Along the edges of the pathway.
There is a lamppost in a wooden fence.
The curb of a street in a city is visible with a blurry background of people walking in the street and on the sidewalk.
The curb is rough and dirty, and there is water next to it.
Small bumps on concrete are shown up close.
A cobblestone or brick street with trolley rails running through the middle is shown.
It is in the middle of a city.
There are gold and trees and pretty buildings along the sides.
A bridge and tall buildings are visible in the background.
A red brick building with an arched opening, and a grand entryway is shown.
There are an ornate railing and stairs leading up to a grand tall door made of wood.
There is ivy growing on the railing.
A large office building is shown. It has large windows all along the front and a big white frame around three sets of double doors.
There are stairs in front in a ramp with railing leading up to the doors.
A beautiful white and tan spiral staircase is shown spiraling down toward lush green vegetation.
The inside of a building is shown.
There are staircases on both sides of a large glass and metal elevator.
Someone is getting ready to use the stairs.
A closeup shot of the metal buttons and labels in an elevator are shown
the label speech, or black backgrounds with white symbols and braille translations.
An exotic white building is shown.
It has ornate railing next to a set of stairs leading up to its entrance.
At street level. A large window and an arched opening for a shop can be seen.
There is an antique bicycle with flowers on it, parked in front of the building.
And There is artwork and flowers on the outer walls.
A person's hand is shown pressing the button of a doorbell.
A woman is shown pushing a grocery cart out the door of a supermarket.
She is walking through a set of automatic sliding doors.
A men's and women's bathroom sign is shown.
And any gender and accessible bathroom sign is shown. It is black and white.
It features a braille transcription of the word bathroom.
A restroom with plenty of extra space and hand rails along the sides is shown.
There is a toilet on the left and a shower on the right.
An old looking water fountain is shown.
A child's hand is pressing on the button, and water is coming out. In a small stream,
the child can barely reach the button.
Drinking fountains at two different heights are shown.
They come out from the wall and do not have protruding bases.
They have large push buttons on the front that are labeled with the word push.
There is a symbol to show that it is for drinking water, and it is written in many different languages.
A small metal water fountain with sensors above it is shown
water is coming out without anyone touching the fountain.
A sleek metal subway train, or magnet train, is headed through the train station.
The station has many people bustling about and is filled with metal and light fixtures.
A large map of a city can be seen.
A busy street with a double decker bus can be seen in the background.
The map features bright colors and many labels.
A subway train is shown.
The doors are painted red, while the body of the train is white.
There are blue hand rails inside the entrance to the train.
A bright, busy subway platform is shown.
There are narrow turnstiles with people going through them.
A grade out image of a city is shown.
Large buildings can be seen in the background.
A bright yellow taxi stands out as it drives across a large metal bridge.
A brand new wheelchair accessible taxi is shown in a showroom.
It has a back hatch open with a ramp extended out the back.
It is black.
There is a wheelchair show next to it.
The back is spacious with plenty of room for the wheelchair.
There are people walking around and viewing the vehicle.
A big touch screen is shown. It features large buttons and text that contrasts with the colors of the buttons.
The taxi fare and extra charges are clearly shown.
There is an audio options button, an info button, an exit button,
and a repeat button.
The same touch screen as before, is shown.
A man is shown relaxing in an airport chair with his legs crossed and propped upon his luggage.
A glass barrier can be seen next to him.
He is watching a plane take off outside the window. Next to him.
Sunlight is filtering in.
The symbol for the creative commons license is shown.

audio_descriptions.notes: A man is shown relaxing in an airport chair with his legs crossed and propped up on his luggage. A glass barrier can be seen next to him. He is watching a plane take off outside the window next to him. Sunlight is filtering in.
